[ul][li]Code[/li] [li]Create Commands[/li] [li]Create No-IP[/li] [li]Make people Mod/Admin[/li][/ul]
If you are interested please PM me as soon as you have read this post!

What’s the point of you even being mod or admin on it, if alls you’ll be doing is playing it?
